==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionDrawCosmCircle3Points''' tool adds a cosmetic circle based on three vertices.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmCircle3PointsExample.png|250px]]
{{Caption|On the right an added cosmetic circle}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select three vertices on the circumference to determine the circle.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmCircle3Points.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmCircle3Points|Cosmetic 3 Point Circle]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmCircle3Points.svg|16px]] Cosmetic 3 Point Circle}} option from the menu.
# A cosmetic circle is added.


